<paragraph id="B182AD64A273DE80384EFAF4B572A10C" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="AC432D378FF775B369F1D1BF48A8A5F9" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Endemic to Jamaica where it gows in mountain woodland.</paragraph>
